overview: On June 3rd, 2008, the country's soon to be new First Couple enjoyed an intimate fist jab in front of a worldwide television audience. The sight of this playful display sent one well-known east coast network news anchor into a tailspin of wild fear and confusion. Many believed it was her televised frenzied panic that propelled one tender moment into "The Fist Bump heard 'Round the World". The true source of loud pounding, thumping, noises encircling the Earth that day was really the four straight days of wild, over the top fisting going on here at Raging Stallion Studios for our latest fisting release: FISTPACK 19 - FIST BUMP.  We brought together a hot new cast of guys and boy, were they hungry and eager to get their hands into each other's holes! There is lots of amazing talent in this cast, to be sure. It's no wonder windows were rattling at Rockefeller Center and beyond.
title: Fistpack 19: Fist Bump
